<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śātakābde śakavaruṣaṁbu 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lu 1347 <unclear>ḍu</unclear> Agunēṁṭi viśvāvasu 
<lb n="3"/>saṁvaccara vaiśākha śu 2 śu taruvakaḷataṁ 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mmā nāyaniṁgāri bhaṁṭṭu mīdi malliseṭṭi ba 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>lumma koṁḍḍamīṁdi śrī narasiṁhya dēvuniki taṁ 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mānāyaniṁgāriki puṇyamugānu 
<lb n="7"/>vupajagati kaṭṭiṁcenu maṁgaḷamahā śrīśrī 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>śrīṁ jēyunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> yāvaccaṁdraśca sū 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ryaścayāvattiṣṭati mēdinī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="10"/>yāvadrāmakathālōkē tā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vadrājyaṁ vibhīṣaṇaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="12"/>nija <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> vīrajasiṁgaya <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="13"/>mallayya śuṁḍu neyya melaraṁga 
<lb n="14"/>viludēyyakelami <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/>dāsapajagatiki te <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> dhammaṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> saketi 
<lb n="16"/>Ācaṁdrātākramuga <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

